768d2ca4daa2db611fd4aeb561701f4e  chromium-dlfcn.patch
76cb0975e631d54fb57bd298041cec05  chromium-yasm.patch
f8c8711a358d43ecbd8e1859aa71cfa0  chromium-no-mit-screensaver.patch
